# Meeting Agenda for Thursday 9th August, 2012

This is the proposed agenda for the SPI board meeting of Thursday,
August 9th, 2012, to be held at 20:00 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.

1. Opening
2. Roll Call
3. President's report (Bdale Garbee)
4. Treasurer's report (Michael Schultheiss)
5. Secretary's report (Jonathan McDowell)
6. Outstanding minutes
   1. [Thursday, 12th July 2012](../../../minutes/2012/2012-07-12/)
      (Jonathan McDowell)
