19. Next board meeting: September 13th, 2012, 20:00 UTC


## President's report

We hosted an SPI BOF at DebConf 12 just after last month's meeting, as with
all DebConf sessions, [video](http://meetings-archive.debian.net/pub/debian-meetings/2012/debconf12/low/847_SPI_BOF.ogv) is available if anyone wants to watch it.

The other real news from me this month is that I'm taking [early retirement from HP](http://www.gag.com/bdale/blog/posts/Early_Retirement.html) at the end of August.


